en_950588_0	A sum of Rs 8 million, collected by the Army through the Poppy Flower campaign in 2018 was handed over to Brigadier A.K Gnanaweera (retd), President, Ex-Servicemen's Association on Friday (15) by Major General Nishantha Wanniarachchi, Adjutant General on behalf of the Commander of the Army.
en_950588_1	After inviting him to the Adjutant General Branch at Narahenpita, Major General Wanniarachchi handed over the cheque to that value.
